e_low":91.1,"long_business_summary":"Alphalogic Industries Limited designs, manufactures, supplies, and installs industrial racks and storage solutions in India. The company offers industrial racks; medium and heavy-duty racks; industrial mezzanine floor; mobile compactor storage systems comprising push and pull type mobile compactors, and motorised and mechanical mobile compactor systems; and staff and cellphone/gadget lockers. It also provides pallet racking systems comprising live pallet racking, double deep pallet racking, and selective racking systems; shelving systems consisting of slotted angle shelving, long span shelving, and multi-tier shelving; and metal pallets, such as cage and flat pallets. In addition, the company offers cantilever racking, slotted angle mezzanine, and column based mezzanine products; and library products, such as library stacks, magazine displays, book return and cases, book supports, newspaper and periodical display racks, magazine holder with drawer, modular compactor storage systems, comprehensive circulation counters, book trolleys, signages, slide to side movable racks, filing and book shelf cabinets, library sitting areas, computer and office tables, revolving chairs, school benches, notice pinup boards, waiting chairs, bunk beds, and storage racks. Further, it provides consultancy, design, installation, and after sales support services. The company serves the automobile industry, libraries, food industry, logistics companies, engineering companies, pharmaceutical organizations, educational institutes, and IT industries, etc. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Pune, India. Alphalogic Industries Limited is a subsidiary of Alphalogic Techsys Limited."}}